# Contribution Guide

Thank you for contributing to this project!

## Structure
- apps/accounts: user profiles (Client, Salon, Reseller)
- apps/salon: services and bookings
- apps/reseller: product catalog
- apps/payments: M-Pesa integration
- apps/delivery: couriers and logistics
- mcp/: AI reporting layer

## Best Practices
- Follow PEP8
- Use migrations for model changes
- Write unit tests for new features
- Clear commit messages (e.g., `feat: add booking model`)

## Pull Request Flow
1. Create branch: `feature/booking-service`
2. Implement and test
3. Open PR with detailed description
